---
title: Harissa Spiced Cannellini Bean Stew with garlic bread and golden fried cheese
description: Garlic bread is one of life's great pleasures. It shines brightest when it's homemade and used for mopping up moreish dishes like this harissa bean stew.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R07_W20_IE_IEXVV0049-4_Main_4_high-3852953b.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.ie/recipecards/card/harissa-spiced-cannelini-bean-stew-6409d6844f1b6a09c1dfc506-a3d3b647.pdf
